data.purchase-link#Purchase link:
The purchase link is automatically generated based on the hierarchical structure of the input file. For files containing multiple variants on a single page, the link includes specific variant parameters in the URL, such as https://www.ashop.com/productPage?var=black_20_male.Parameter name is defined as reservedNames.product.varientParameterName in rjs.config.json. Configure this according to your web server's logic of parameters handling.
  {
    "reservedNames": {
      "product": {
      "varientParameterName": "var"
      }
    }
  }

